LEColorPicker: generates a color scheme from an icon, similar to iTunes.  This algorithm provides a badge color as well as a contrasting text color.

Boover: calculates an average color for an icon, ignoring bright pixels.  This algorithm provides just a badge color.

ColorBadges: generates a badge color for an icon using the ColorBadges API.  Requires ColorBadges to be installed, otherwise default iOS colors will be used.  This algorithm provides just a badge color.";

